      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 20 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 20 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>觀，盥而不荐，有孚顒若。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Guan shows (how he whom it represents should be like) the worshipper who has washed his hands, but not (yet) presented his offerings - with sincerity and an appearance of dignity (commanding reverent regard).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
