      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 20 初六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六：童觀，小人无咎，君子吝。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, shows the looking of a lad - not blamable in men of inferior rank, but matter for regret in superior men.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
