      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六二：窺觀，利女貞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second SIX, divided, shows one peeping out from a door. It would be advantageous if it were (merely) the firm correctness of a female.</seg>
